[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man, 31, dies after attack in Gorbals flat

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been arrested by police following the death of a man in a flat in the Gorbals area of Glasgow.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to the Waddell Court high-rise flats at about 18:30 on Monday over reports a man had been assaulted.
A 31-year man was taken to Glasgow Royal Infirmary, but died a short time later.
Police said on Tuesday evening that a 55-year-old man had been detained over the incident.
He is expected to appear at Glasgow Sheriff Court on Wednesday.
